Reference: http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Cricket_statistics


Batting Statisics:
Innings (ODI): The number of matches in which the player actually batted. 
Batting Averge (ODI): The total number of runs scored by a player divided by the total number of matches in which the player batted. 


Bowling Statisics:
Bolwing Average: The average number of runs conceded per wicket.





